00:41.174 --> 00:42.375
DANIEL: That's right.

00:51.652 --> 00:53.554
BOTH: Disco sucks!

01:02.596 --> 01:05.431
Oh... my... God.

01:13.540 --> 01:16.342
<i>♪♪ I don't give a damn</i>
<i>'bout my reputation</i>

01:18.178 --> 01:20.714
<i>♪♪ Livin' in the past,</i>
